{"tid":560654,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"冬奧支那成隊滑冰俾泡菜黑撚走晒","createTime":"2018-02-14T09:34:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-14T09:54:08.000Z","uid":26769,"like":11,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1c3000ddfee52c5d64f146ec3e11db794adf89d2","tid":560654,"uid":26769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T09:34:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180214/57831608\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180214%2F57831608&d=2NT3ILbaMCQiFHNmecbQxv%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=9b96b70d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180214%2F57831608&h=cdf75ae9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180214/57831608</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c58f4ba90bbff6014e5c6f7e24a074669860c469","tid":560654,"uid":63909,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T09:36:17.000Z","msg":"咩中文黎？"},{"pid":"0e750c21a690a7629f4ec17ee1253349ba9c16c2","tid":560654,"uid":149363,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T09:39:40.000Z","msg":"韓狗真係賤畜民族"},{"pid":"29b3a01c948284310ed3ab5f2240c74331d2e1f2","tid":560654,"uid":531,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T09:43:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">不過，官方新華社報道，李琰事後談到這些爭議判罰時表示，總的來說還是中國隊沒有做好自己。李琰說：「今天的1,000米男隊打得積極主動，初衷就是減少失誤和犯規的可能性，因為競爭比較激烈。沒想到任子威和韓天宇最終衝過終點線時是qualified（晉級的），但是過程中沒有做得那麼完美，還是讓裁判找到了毛病。女子范可新和曲春雨初賽表現不錯，范可新第二次（參加）奧運會，應該這樣講，自己的水準還是沒有發揮出來，挺遺憾的。曲春雨第一次奧運會，一直敢打敢拼，打到現在這個位置上（已經不容易了）。」</span><br />\n<br />\n廢就廢，關咩黑事"},{"pid":"96dee5dfd6dac4063e884e819369913bd8c28de3","tid":560654,"uid":23525,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T09:44:39.000Z","msg":"黑你老母"},{"pid":"beca8250cd22249deb084058d424734488976847","tid":560654,"uid":23635,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T09:48:49.000Z","msg":"強国攞唔到奬牌：評判偏幫<br />\n強国好彩攞到奬牌：實力表現<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfd79d360e76d21038b44031c84212b9ef8cec7a","tid":560654,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T09:49:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pic.pimg.tw/mulicia/bcefbb013a28dd3a2eabd6a9a18e5ae6_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fmulicia%2Fbcefbb013a28dd3a2eabd6a9a18e5ae6_n.jpg&h=810979d0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dde49e7c705d1a5e9a00d228521a3839fcb7a5cb","tid":560654,"uid":14246,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T09:54:08.000Z","msg":"是但啦垃圾對垃圾"}]}